{isExpanded && (

🔄 Current Implementation

Our app opens grocery apps/websites with ingredients pre-loaded in the search, but you'll need to manually add items to your cart.

🚫 Why Direct Cart Addition Isn't Available

  • No Public APIs: Grocery apps don't provide public cart APIs
  • Security Restrictions: Cart operations require user authentication
  • App Store Policies: Direct cart manipulation is restricted

✅ What We Do Instead

  • Smart Search: Pre-load ingredients in search bar
  • Deep Links: Open mobile apps directly
  • Web Integration: Open web apps with search queries
  • Ingredient List: Show exact quantities and units

🔮 Future Possibilities

  • Official Partnerships: Work with grocery apps for API access
  • User Authentication: Allow users to connect their accounts
  • Price Comparison: Show prices across different apps
  • Order Tracking: Track grocery orders

💡 Pro Tips

  • Use the ingredient list as a shopping checklist
  • Compare prices across different grocery apps
  • Save frequently used ingredients for quick access
  • Check for delivery slots before ordering
)}
); }; export default CartLimitationsGuide;
